To execute a health check for Prometheus, I will use the `health_check` function. Here is how you can invoke it:

```json
{
  "type": "function",
  "function": {
    "name": "prometheus.health_check",
    "description": "Health check endpoint for container monitoring and status verification"
  }
}
```

Please execute this JSON payload to perform the health check. Once completed, I will provide you with only the result of that operation.
